  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA16">
<l>taṉakkaṭimaip paṭṭatu tāṉaṟiyā ṉēlu</l>
<l>maṉattaṭaiya vaippatā mālai – vaṉattiṭarai</l>
<l>yēriyām vaṇṇa miyaṟṟu mituvallāṉ</l>
<l>māriyār peykiṟpār maṟṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Falling in servitude to him, even if one does not know it,</l>
<l>is holding Māl so that he is close to [one’s] mind. Except for this</l>  
<l>when one acts in a manner that a sand bank in the forest may become a lake,</l>
<l>who else will be able  to pour the rain?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
